{"data":[{"id":563904977,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":307595822,"title":"高中生对哥德巴赫猜想的证明有哪些错误？","question_type":"normal","created":1546272354,"updated_time":1546301579,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0769528fa3b24c8c6a92d3645b2ab1f1","url_token":"","name":"知乎用户","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":2,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":true},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563904977","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546309712,"updated_time":1546309712,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":8,"comment_count":3,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e我确定我已掌握作者想法。在此修改其表述如下：（以情况1为例）\u003c/p\u003e\u003cblockquote\u003e准备：\u003cbr\u003e1.设正质数的集合为P+，设集合P。 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=P_%7B%2B%7D%5Csubseteq+P\" alt=\"P_{+}\\subseteq P\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e \u003cbr\u003e2.设集合 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=A%3D%5C%7B2n%7Cn%5Cin+N_%7B%2B%7D%5Cwedge2n%3Da%2Bb%2Ca%5Cin+P%2Cb%5Cin+P%5C%7D%2CB%3D%5C%7B2n%7Cn%5Cin+N_%7B%2B%7D%5Cwedge2n%3Da%2Bb%2Ca%5Cin+P_%7B%2B%7D%2Cb%5Cin+P_%7B%2B%7D%5C%7D\" alt=\"A=\\{2n|n\\in N_{+}\\wedge2n=a+b,a\\in P,b\\in P\\},B=\\{2n|n\\in N_{+}\\wedge2n=a+b,a\\in P_{+},b\\in P_{+}\\}\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e \u003cbr\u003e3.欲证情况1： \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Cforall+k%5Cin+N_%7B%2B%7D%2C%286k%2B2%29%5Cin+B\" alt=\"\\forall k\\in N_{+},(6k+2)\\in B\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e \u003c/blockquote\u003e\u003cp\u003e证明：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cblockquote\u003e命题1：\u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Cforall+n%5Cin+N_%7B%2B%7D%2C2n%5Cin+B%E6%88%962n%3D%28-1%29%2B%282n%2B1%29%2C2n%2B1%5Cin+P_%7B%2B%7D\" alt=\"\\forall n\\in N_{+},2n\\in B或2n=(-1)+(2n+1),2n+1\\in P_{+}\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e \u003cbr\u003e命题2： \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%E8%8B%A5-1%5Cin+P%2C%E5%88%99%5Cforall+n%5Cin+N_%7B%2B%7D%282n%5Cin+A%29\" alt=\"若-1\\in P,则\\forall n\\in N_{+}(2n\\in A)\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e \u003cbr\u003e对命题2取逆否命题，得到命题3： \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%E8%8B%A5%5Cexists+n_%7B0%7D%5Cin+N_%7B%2B%7D%282n_%7B0%7D%5Cnotin+A%29%2C%E5%88%99-1%5Cnotin+P\" alt=\"若\\exists n_{0}\\in N_{+}(2n_{0}\\notin A),则-1\\notin P\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e \u003cbr\u003e在命题3中取 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=n_%7B0%7D%3D1\" alt=\"n_{0}=1\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e ，得到命题4： \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%E8%8B%A52%5Cnotin+A%EF%BC%8C%E5%88%99-1%5Cnotin+P\" alt=\"若2\\notin A，则-1\\notin P\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e \u003c/blockquote\u003e\u003cp\u003e∵2=(-1)+3\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e∴命题4为真。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e∴命题3为真。//错在这里。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e∵命题2是命题3的逆否命题。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e∴命题2为真。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e∵在命题2的结论中，仅有两种情况： \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=2n%5Cin+B%E6%88%962n%3D%28-1%29%2B%282n%2B1%29%2C2n%2B1%5Cin+P_%7B%2B%7D\" alt=\"2n\\in B或2n=(-1)+(2n+1),2n+1\\in P_{+}\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e∴命题1为真。//这里偷懒了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Cforall+k%5Cin+N_%7B%2B%7D\" alt=\"\\forall k\\in N_{+}\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e ，应用命题1，得： \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%286k%2B2%29%5Cin+B%E6%88%966k%2B2%3D%28-1%29%2B%286k%2B3%29%2C%286k%2B3%29%5Cin+P_%7B%2B%7D\" alt=\"(6k+2)\\in B或6k+2=(-1)+(6k+3),(6k+3)\\in P_{+}\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e其中 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%286k%2B3%29%5Cin+P_%7B%2B%7D\" alt=\"(6k+3)\\in P_{+}\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 不成立，故只能是 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%286k%2B2%29%5Cin+B\" alt=\"(6k+2)\\in B\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e \u003c/p\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003e由此可见，什么负质数、-1是质数、恒等式都不是问题。问题在于命题4的前提比命题3强，那么对于这两个假言命题来说，命题4反而比命题3弱，故命题4为真不能推导出命题3为真。\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"我确定我已掌握作者想法。在此修改其表述如下：（以情况1为例）准备： 1.设正质数的集合为P+，设集合P。 P_{+}\\subseteq P 2.设集合 A=\\{2n|n\\in N_{+}\\wedge2n=a+b,a\\in P,b\\in P\\},B=\\{2n|n\\in N_{+}\\wedge2n=a+b,a\\in P_{+},b\\in P_{+}\\} 3.欲证情况1： …","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=79\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Canno